WEBVTT

01:51.640 --> 01:53.200
Ms. Xu, your outfit is so pretty.

01:53.200 --> 01:54.200
Where did you buy it?

01:54.200 --> 01:55.400
A friend gave it to me.

01:55.400 --> 01:57.640
Don't tell me it's from your boyfriend.

01:57.720 --> 01:58.560
No.

02:01.560 --> 02:02.840
There's a movie coming out this Saturday

02:02.840 --> 02:04.240
called 'Secret'.

02:04.600 --> 02:06.000
I heard it's really good.

02:06.160 --> 02:07.640
I don't have time to go.

02:07.720 --> 02:09.050
I'm busy this Saturday.

02:09.919 --> 02:11.320
I have time to watch it,

02:12.240 --> 02:13.040
but

02:13.680 --> 02:15.160
I need someone to go with.

02:22.400 --> 02:23.260
Time for class.

02:23.920 --> 02:24.480
I'm off.

02:25.280 --> 02:26.740
Ms. Xu, I'm going to class.

02:27.200 --> 02:28.520
Okay. I don't have a class this period.

02:28.520 --> 02:29.680
I'll prepare my lessons here.

02:29.680 --> 02:30.520
Okay.

02:36.360 --> 02:37.120
Ms. Xu,

02:37.600 --> 02:38.440
after preparing your lessons,

02:38.440 --> 02:39.500
stretch your neck.

02:39.640 --> 02:40.640
It's good for you.

02:41.280 --> 02:41.800
Thanks.

02:41.880 --> 02:42.640
I'm going to class.

02:42.640 --> 02:43.200
Okay.

03:00.560 --> 03:02.120
There's a movie coming out this Saturday

03:02.120 --> 03:03.520
called "Secret".

03:29.360 --> 03:30.400
Please welcome

03:30.480 --> 03:32.410
the popular actress Xiong Yuanbao

03:32.440 --> 03:33.640
to the stage.

03:45.480 --> 03:46.640
Thank you, everyone. Thank you.

03:46.640 --> 03:47.680
Thank you all.

03:47.760 --> 03:48.890
No need for flowers.

03:49.160 --> 03:50.690
Thank you for the applause.

03:50.840 --> 03:51.480
First of all,

03:51.480 --> 03:53.200
I want to thank my parents

03:53.360 --> 03:55.400
for giving me such an artistic talent.

03:55.400 --> 03:56.600
Then I also want to thank

03:56.600 --> 03:57.400
my fans

03:57.400 --> 03:58.680
for their enthusiastic support.

03:58.680 --> 04:00.210
Thank you, my dear friends.

04:00.240 --> 04:01.360
Thank you, everyone.

04:01.360 --> 04:02.290
You are too kind.

04:02.320 --> 04:03.000
Have a seat. Have a seat.

04:03.000 --> 04:04.000
You are too kind.

04:04.040 --> 04:05.320
Too kind. Too kind.

04:09.600 --> 04:10.800
When did you get here?

04:12.240 --> 04:13.970
No, how long have you been here?

04:14.240 --> 04:15.770
Since your grand entrance.

04:22.160 --> 04:24.420
Your acceptance speech was pretty good.

04:24.880 --> 04:26.200
You're too kind.

04:27.040 --> 04:28.480
This is pretty awkward.

04:32.520 --> 04:34.920
Back at Peiying,

04:35.440 --> 04:36.840
whenever we had PE class,

04:37.159 --> 04:39.420
I'd come to the rooftop to enjoy the view.

04:40.360 --> 04:41.840
Now at Zhicheng,

04:42.720 --> 04:45.080
I didn't expect to meet a kindred spirit.

04:46.880 --> 04:48.480
When Mutou and I were little,

04:48.520 --> 04:50.320
we loved playing on the rooftop.

04:50.600 --> 04:52.000
But he is afraid of heights,

04:52.000 --> 04:53.360
so I always liked to scare him.

04:53.360 --> 04:54.800
If he didn't listen to me,

04:55.159 --> 04:58.020
I'd lock him on the roof and wouldn't let him go home.

04:58.680 --> 05:00.540
Seems like you two are very close.

05:00.680 --> 05:01.920
We grew up together.

05:12.760 --> 05:14.160
What are you laughing at?

05:26.880 --> 05:27.600
Don't move.

05:41.840 --> 05:42.800
There is a leaf.

05:47.520 --> 05:48.380
There's a leaf.

05:49.320 --> 05:50.080
Damn.

05:51.320 --> 05:52.180
Going to study.

06:06.960 --> 06:07.800
Ms. Xu,

06:08.400 --> 06:09.400
getting off work?

06:09.920 --> 06:10.640
Yes.

06:16.880 --> 06:18.140
Why is your face so red?

06:18.600 --> 06:19.480
Are you sick?

06:34.920 --> 06:37.480
See you at the cinema this weekend.

06:37.840 --> 06:40.500
From someone who has admired you for a long time.

06:47.880 --> 06:48.560
I...

06:48.840 --> 06:50.570
Why is my heart beating so fast?

06:53.640 --> 06:54.760
You don't understand.

06:54.760 --> 06:56.220
I am no longer an immortal.

06:56.720 --> 06:57.280
I...

07:01.520 --> 07:02.780
You don't understand.

07:02.920 --> 07:04.240
I am no longer...

07:08.720 --> 07:10.000
You don't understand.

07:13.840 --> 07:15.240
You...

07:20.480 --> 07:22.280
Have some fruit and take a break.

07:25.280 --> 07:26.210
I don't want any.

07:27.840 --> 07:28.600
I mean,

07:29.160 --> 07:30.360
just let it go.

07:30.560 --> 07:31.760
You can't win anyway.

07:31.960 --> 07:33.040
Just act casually.

07:33.280 --> 07:34.680
Why are you so depressed?

07:35.360 --> 07:36.560
You really are a jinx.

07:36.760 --> 07:37.440
I knew it.

07:37.440 --> 07:39.440
You never have anything nice to say.

07:40.600 --> 07:41.360
Look at you.

07:41.800 --> 07:44.720
You've been doing nothing but studying and practicing lines,

07:44.720 --> 07:46.380
but why are you getting worse?

07:46.640 --> 07:48.000
Are you too tired?

07:48.440 --> 07:49.600
I don't know either.

07:50.440 --> 07:53.000
The more anxious I get, the worse I memorize.

07:55.640 --> 07:56.520
Alright.

07:57.320 --> 07:59.050
Why don't you take a break today

08:00.040 --> 08:01.200
and clear your mind?

08:01.560 --> 08:02.760
I'll take you to a movie.

08:02.760 --> 08:03.560
You need to balance work and rest.

08:03.560 --> 08:05.420
I'm not going. I'm not in the mood.

08:05.560 --> 08:07.440
Don't you want to go to the cinema

08:07.560 --> 08:09.840
to observe how others act?

08:10.240 --> 08:10.920
Besides,

08:12.000 --> 08:13.720
it stars Jay Chou.

08:15.520 --> 08:16.360
Jay Chou?

08:17.680 --> 08:18.520
Not bad.

08:18.800 --> 08:20.360
Hello, I'm Jay Chou.

08:21.200 --> 08:22.130
Do you want to go?

08:24.640 --> 08:26.370
You should've told me earlier.

08:26.960 --> 08:27.720
When?

08:28.320 --> 08:29.880
You go out first. I need to change.

08:29.880 --> 08:30.640
Hurry!

08:55.760 --> 08:56.720
Hello, Mr. Xu.

08:57.960 --> 08:58.920
Mr. Xu is here.

09:04.600 --> 09:05.720
It's all your fault.

09:05.720 --> 09:07.000
Why did we have to wait for the 315?

09:07.000 --> 09:09.060
If we took the 414, we'd be here by now.

09:09.160 --> 09:09.920
What's the rush?

09:09.920 --> 09:11.720
There's still a line over there.

09:11.720 --> 09:12.400
Hurry up.

09:13.280 --> 09:14.440
Two buckets of popcorn.

09:14.440 --> 09:15.040
Wait a minute.

09:15.040 --> 09:15.840
Hurry and pay.

09:19.200 --> 09:20.080
Don't rush.

09:20.480 --> 09:21.410
What's the rush?

09:37.880 --> 09:38.680
Mr. Xu.

09:39.800 --> 09:40.520
Hello.

10:02.880 --> 10:04.600
Why are these two kids here?

10:05.640 --> 10:07.720
If they find out I'm watching a movie with Mr. Xu,

10:07.720 --> 10:08.980
it would be so awkward.

10:35.080 --> 10:35.940
Excuse me, sir.

10:36.200 --> 10:37.600
Are you in the wrong seat?

10:39.400 --> 10:40.320
Mr. Tian.

10:42.680 --> 10:43.680
Tian Yong.

10:46.120 --> 10:47.160
Mr. Liu Li.

11:02.240 --> 11:03.160
Well,

11:03.680 --> 11:05.160
Mr. Liu and I are just

11:05.240 --> 11:07.720
doing a surprise inspection at the movie theater today,

11:07.720 --> 11:08.400
to see if there are any

11:08.400 --> 11:10.730
boys and girls watching movies together.

11:10.760 --> 11:12.400
And I actually caught a pair.

11:12.680 --> 11:14.280
Yes, exactly.

11:14.720 --> 11:16.640
Well, Mr. Tian, Mr. Liu.

11:17.000 --> 11:19.840
We've been studying all morning.

11:20.000 --> 11:20.600
Really.

11:20.840 --> 11:22.720
Isn't the drama festival coming up soon?

11:22.720 --> 11:25.200
We just wanted to strike a balance between work and rest,

11:25.200 --> 11:27.040
so we came out to watch a movie.

11:27.240 --> 11:27.920
To learn.

11:28.040 --> 11:28.920
To learn.

11:29.440 --> 11:29.960
Right.

11:30.680 --> 11:31.360
Well,

11:31.480 --> 11:33.680
since that's the case, it's excusable.

11:34.400 --> 11:35.530
They are still kids.

11:35.800 --> 11:37.320
They're childhood sweethearts,

11:37.320 --> 11:38.520
so it's normal for them to be playful.

11:38.520 --> 11:39.120
Right?

11:39.360 --> 11:41.560
Mr. Tian, I think we should just drop this.

11:41.560 --> 11:43.360
Let's all go our separate ways.

11:43.400 --> 11:44.560
Hurry up and leave.

11:44.720 --> 11:45.600
Are you waiting for me to scold you?

11:45.600 --> 11:47.720
Okay, goodbye, sir.

11:47.760 --> 11:48.440
Thank you.

11:49.160 --> 11:49.920
Let's go.

12:02.040 --> 12:03.000
You're right.

12:03.080 --> 12:04.280
Go that way.

12:04.360 --> 12:05.040
That way.

12:08.440 --> 12:10.760
I'm so lucky to see such a scene in my life.

12:11.120 --> 12:13.520
The movie doesn't even matter anymore.

12:14.400 --> 12:18.060
What are you thinking about every day in that little head of yours?

12:20.480 --> 12:21.320
Say,

12:21.800 --> 12:23.640
if one day in the future,

12:24.360 --> 12:25.960
we could also make movies...

12:26.760 --> 12:28.160
If the movies we made

12:28.520 --> 12:30.050
could be shown in theaters,

12:30.600 --> 12:31.920
how would that feel?

12:34.000 --> 12:34.720
What?

12:35.320 --> 12:36.840
Do you want to be an actor

12:36.840 --> 12:37.900
or a screenwriter?

12:38.520 --> 12:40.050
A screenwriter, of course.

12:40.520 --> 12:42.520
But I need to understand actors too.

12:43.200 --> 12:44.400
If one day,

12:44.880 --> 12:46.240
a movie I wrote

12:46.960 --> 12:48.760
could be shown on the big screen,

12:49.160 --> 12:51.360
I would wake up laughing from my dreams.

12:56.240 --> 12:59.920
So do you really like 'A Chinese Odyssey' this time,

13:00.560 --> 13:03.320
or is it because of that Meng Jingu?

13:04.200 --> 13:07.730
First of all, of course it's because I like 'A Chinese Odyssey'.

13:08.000 --> 13:09.120
But secondly,

13:09.280 --> 13:10.800
if I could act with someone

13:10.880 --> 13:13.680
as excellent as Meng Jingu,

13:14.480 --> 13:15.920
that would be great too.

13:21.200 --> 13:22.360
However...

13:26.480 --> 13:27.320
Mutou,

13:28.600 --> 13:29.720
tell me,

13:30.680 --> 13:32.480
am I really useless?

13:36.720 --> 13:39.380
Why would you suddenly say that about yourself?

13:45.840 --> 13:48.560
Look, I've been memorizing for so many days,

13:49.160 --> 13:51.120
yet I can't even remember a few lines,

13:51.120 --> 13:52.840
let alone perform on stage.

13:53.360 --> 13:54.560
I suddenly feel

13:55.400 --> 13:57.130
like I can't do anything right.

13:59.040 --> 14:01.160
All I do is daydream all day.

14:07.360 --> 14:09.120
Yuanbao, don't cry.

14:09.560 --> 14:11.490
You're not as bad as you say you are.

14:14.760 --> 14:17.620
You said this morning that I would definitely lose.

14:18.360 --> 14:20.440
Actually, I feel the same way.

14:21.400 --> 14:23.600
Actually, I was just kidding, Yuanbao.

14:25.240 --> 14:26.480
You are really great.

14:26.560 --> 14:28.360
You have to believe in yourself.

14:28.760 --> 14:30.680
Do you remember when we were in junior high

14:30.680 --> 14:32.120
and performed a magic trick together?

14:32.120 --> 14:34.880
I remember you were so nervous before going on stage,

14:34.880 --> 14:37.600
but you performed really well once you were up there.

14:37.600 --> 14:40.080
You've just been putting too much pressure on yourself lately.

14:40.080 --> 14:42.480
You want to do too well in this performance.

14:43.920 --> 14:44.720
Really?

14:45.080 --> 14:46.160
Of course.

14:46.680 --> 14:47.560
Listen to me.

14:48.040 --> 14:50.200
I'll teach you how to relax your face.

14:58.840 --> 15:00.920
I see actors before going on stage

15:00.960 --> 15:02.760
doing these facial relaxation

15:02.800 --> 15:03.440
and

15:04.800 --> 15:05.840
warm-up exercises.

15:05.840 --> 15:07.040
Come on, do it with me.

15:16.040 --> 15:17.100
Do you feel better?

15:18.680 --> 15:20.480
How about this, I'll practice with you.

15:20.480 --> 15:23.080
Even if it's last-minute, it might still help.

15:23.280 --> 15:26.040
Aren't you acting with Xing Yaqi?

15:26.240 --> 15:28.640
Why are you willing to practice with me now?

15:29.280 --> 15:31.000
I'm trying to help you, aren't I?

15:31.000 --> 15:32.440
Are you going to practice or not?

15:32.440 --> 15:33.240
I will.

15:33.840 --> 15:34.760
But...

15:35.320 --> 15:37.080
there are so many people here.

15:39.200 --> 15:40.960
Isn't a performance meant to be seen by everyone?

15:40.960 --> 15:42.320
It's also a good way to build your courage.

15:42.320 --> 15:43.680
Come on, I'll start.

15:44.280 --> 15:46.480
Once there was a sincere love

15:46.480 --> 15:47.480
placed before me,

15:48.080 --> 15:49.410
but I didn't cherish it.

15:50.480 --> 15:51.920
Zhi Zunbao, wait for me.

15:51.960 --> 15:54.080
I only regretted it after losing it.

15:54.320 --> 15:56.780
There is nothing more painful in this world.

15:56.880 --> 15:58.720
Just cut my throat with your blade.

15:58.720 --> 15:59.920
What?

16:00.280 --> 16:01.720
What are your next lines?

16:01.800 --> 16:02.930
I don't know either.

16:15.600 --> 16:16.840
Grandma.

16:17.520 --> 16:19.180
Why are there so many bottles?

16:19.240 --> 16:20.920
The price of plastic has gone up recently.

16:20.920 --> 16:22.200
I need to collect more.

16:22.240 --> 16:24.170
I can sell them for a lot more money.

16:25.840 --> 16:26.640
I'll help you.

16:26.960 --> 16:28.020
I'll help Grandma.

16:28.160 --> 16:29.290
You help carry this.

17:12.000 --> 17:13.960
Grandma, just give it to me.

17:16.000 --> 17:16.720
Come on.

17:17.040 --> 17:18.599
Young people nowadays

17:18.680 --> 17:20.210
don't know how to do chores.

17:20.560 --> 17:21.560
Trust me, Grandma.

17:21.560 --> 17:22.640
I can do it.

17:24.680 --> 17:25.280
Go.

17:25.599 --> 17:26.560
Go study.

17:27.359 --> 17:29.280
Grandma, I'm done with my homework.

17:29.280 --> 17:30.480
You've been busy all day.

17:30.480 --> 17:31.000
Leave it to me.

17:31.000 --> 17:32.480
Take a good rest, okay?

17:32.840 --> 17:33.880
Oh, you child.

17:33.920 --> 17:36.320
Your focus right now should be on studying.

17:37.760 --> 17:38.520
Grandma.

17:38.800 --> 17:39.660
Grandma, look.

17:39.760 --> 17:40.720
Your precious granddaughter

17:40.720 --> 17:42.650
has prepared the footbath for you.

17:43.920 --> 17:44.800
Go ahead.

17:50.080 --> 17:51.800
How's the water temperature?

17:51.920 --> 17:52.880
Just right.

17:55.480 --> 17:57.320
My Yuanbao has grown up.

17:57.800 --> 17:59.800
You know how to care for Grandma now.

17:59.920 --> 18:00.880
Of course.

18:01.080 --> 18:02.840
Grandma is my goddess.

18:04.560 --> 18:07.040
Yes, we are all goddesses.

18:07.840 --> 18:09.920
You are a little goddess.

18:10.360 --> 18:12.560
And Grandma is an old goddess.

18:17.080 --> 18:17.940
Do you remember

18:18.600 --> 18:20.960
when you couldn't sleep as a child,

18:21.480 --> 18:23.120
Grandma would sing to you?

18:24.880 --> 18:30.080
The moon is bright, the wind is still.

18:30.800 --> 18:35.560
Leaves cover the window lattice.

18:36.440 --> 18:41.520
The little baby is called Zhengzheng.

18:42.080 --> 18:47.000
Quickly close your eyes.

18:47.840 --> 18:52.960
The wind is still, the moon is bright.

18:53.320 --> 18:57.760
The cradle swings gently.

19:00.560 --> 19:01.720
You've been

19:02.080 --> 19:03.410
in a bad mood these days.

19:03.480 --> 19:04.600
I failed my exam.

19:04.760 --> 19:07.220
When my mom beat me that day, her wig fell off.

19:07.440 --> 19:10.120
I just realized she's been wearing a wig for so long.

19:10.120 --> 19:11.850
Her hair loss is quite serious.

19:15.320 --> 19:17.680
Then you should study hard from now on

19:18.120 --> 19:19.720
and make your mom worry less.

19:21.800 --> 19:22.930
I've made up my mind.

19:24.120 --> 19:26.160
I'll play fewer games from now on.

19:27.320 --> 19:28.840
You sounded so determined,

19:28.840 --> 19:31.440
I thought you were going to quit playing games.

19:32.120 --> 19:33.920
That would be so boring.

19:36.200 --> 19:37.660
Bro, let's talk about you.

19:37.760 --> 19:38.960
The roles are about to be cast.

19:38.960 --> 19:40.160
Are you sure?

19:43.080 --> 19:44.960
To prevent Yuanbao from acting with Meng Jingu,

19:44.960 --> 19:46.440
you've taken a lot of trouble.

19:46.440 --> 19:47.440
What if

19:47.840 --> 19:50.040
Yuanbao really can't play Fairy Zixia?

19:50.560 --> 19:51.760
Will she be sad?

19:53.000 --> 19:54.600
I'm also worried about this.

19:54.800 --> 19:57.080
Let me say something unpleasant.

19:58.520 --> 19:59.120
Go ahead.

19:59.360 --> 20:00.840
You are just jealous.

20:01.640 --> 20:03.280
That's really unpleasant.

20:03.720 --> 20:04.520
Envy?

20:05.080 --> 20:05.800
Jealousy?

20:06.240 --> 20:07.320
Of Meng Jingu?

20:08.160 --> 20:10.120
Are you out of your mind?

20:11.000 --> 20:12.920
He's just taller and more handsome,

20:12.920 --> 20:13.980
has better grades,

20:14.760 --> 20:16.040
and comes from a better family.

20:16.040 --> 20:17.280
I used to go to the same school as him.

20:17.280 --> 20:18.680
He is quite a good person.

20:18.840 --> 20:20.520
Last time, it was close to the monthly exam

20:20.520 --> 20:22.000
when you gave Yuanbao the review materials.

20:22.000 --> 20:23.200
What about this time?

20:23.360 --> 20:24.120
Go quickly.

20:24.480 --> 20:25.280
If it doesn't work,

20:25.280 --> 20:27.610
just send it to her anonymously via email.

20:28.040 --> 20:31.280
Didn't you ask me to come over to discuss countermeasures?

20:31.280 --> 20:32.410
Then... I'll leave.

20:38.840 --> 20:39.400
Hello.

20:39.600 --> 20:41.060
Is this Cool Bear's house?

20:41.080 --> 20:43.600
Yes, I'm Cool Bear's grandmother.

20:43.640 --> 20:44.640
Here is your package.

20:44.640 --> 20:45.480
Thank you.

20:48.760 --> 20:52.240
Cool Bear, your package.

20:52.280 --> 20:53.480
What is it, Grandma?

20:53.640 --> 20:55.500
It's yours. Why are you asking me?

21:04.040 --> 21:05.240
Put this on,

21:05.760 --> 21:08.290
and you'll be the most beautiful Fairy Zixia.

21:09.000 --> 21:09.960
I look forward to

21:11.120 --> 21:13.580
Yuanbao's version of Fairy Zixia even more.

21:28.480 --> 21:30.160
Come on, Yuanbao.

21:30.280 --> 21:32.120
Looking forward to your performance tomorrow.

21:32.120 --> 21:34.120
I chose a few good clips

21:34.520 --> 21:35.960
and printed out the corresponding lines.

21:35.960 --> 21:36.840
Take a look.

21:37.520 --> 21:38.920
I know an acting coach.

21:39.080 --> 21:40.540
Are you free after school?

21:40.800 --> 21:42.240
I can ask her to give you some guidance.

21:42.240 --> 21:43.300
Let's go together.

21:45.840 --> 21:47.640
Meng Jingu is so thoughtful.

21:49.000 --> 21:50.440
Thank you, desk mate.

21:50.520 --> 21:51.240
You are awesome.

21:51.240 --> 21:52.170
I will do my best.

21:58.840 --> 22:00.680
Okay, I will let you go.

22:00.960 --> 22:02.400
But you must kiss me.

22:08.440 --> 22:10.480
Jingu, stop playing with your phone.

22:10.480 --> 22:12.140
I have something to say to you.

22:12.200 --> 22:14.520
Your freshman year is coming to an end soon.

22:14.520 --> 22:17.200
You'll also be divided into arts and science classes soon.

22:17.200 --> 22:19.280
I communicated with your homeroom teacher.

22:19.280 --> 22:20.720
With your current grades,

22:20.720 --> 22:22.840
getting into the top science class won't be a problem.

22:22.840 --> 22:25.120
Since you dislike finance so much,

22:25.680 --> 22:27.120
I won't force you.

22:27.720 --> 22:29.720
I am an open-minded father.

22:31.000 --> 22:32.960
Since you want to study physics,

22:33.240 --> 22:34.760
I will respect your wishes.

22:34.760 --> 22:35.560
Really?

22:36.360 --> 22:37.160
However,

22:37.640 --> 22:38.920
I have a condition.

22:39.560 --> 22:40.680
My requirement is

22:41.240 --> 22:43.770
that you must become the top science student.

22:44.120 --> 22:46.080
My son can only be first,

22:46.320 --> 22:47.160
never second.

22:47.960 --> 22:48.760
Got it?

22:52.880 --> 22:55.120
Quiet down, class.

22:55.800 --> 22:57.480
We'll use this study hall

22:58.080 --> 23:00.280
to vote and decide

23:00.440 --> 23:02.360
on the roles for the drama competition.

23:02.360 --> 23:03.620
I'll give you 5 minutes

23:03.680 --> 23:04.520
to prepare,

23:04.640 --> 23:05.640
then we'll start.

23:06.120 --> 23:06.840
Okay.

23:08.160 --> 23:10.040
Don't be nervous. Relax.

23:19.200 --> 23:20.660
Mu Qingjun isn't here yet.

23:23.200 --> 23:24.200
All right, class.

23:24.240 --> 23:26.100
Our first group is going on stage.

23:28.600 --> 23:29.800
You insolent monkey.

23:31.200 --> 23:33.640
To marry the Bull Demon King's sister.

23:40.560 --> 23:41.600
Why are you here?

23:41.920 --> 23:43.720
You're talking nonsense again.

23:43.880 --> 23:45.160
You're talking nonsense again.

23:45.160 --> 23:49.280
Next, please welcome Xiong Yuanbao and Meng Jingu to the stage.

23:49.960 --> 23:50.960
Don't be nervous.

24:05.120 --> 24:06.400
Not bad.

24:11.680 --> 24:13.410
Yuanbao, this is so beautiful.

24:13.840 --> 24:14.960
Zhi Zunbao, you bastard.

24:14.960 --> 24:15.760
Come out here!

24:24.240 --> 24:25.080
Zhi Zunbao!

24:25.760 --> 24:26.720
You bastard!

24:27.240 --> 24:28.280
Come out here!

24:29.320 --> 24:30.360
I'm right here.

24:35.440 --> 24:37.170
It seems I shouldn't have come.

24:37.640 --> 24:39.500
It's too late to realize that now.

24:39.880 --> 24:41.480
Can't we leave some memories?

24:41.480 --> 24:43.080
I don't want to leave memories.

24:43.080 --> 24:46.010
If you want to leave something, leave yourself here.

24:48.000 --> 24:48.840
Okay.

24:49.280 --> 24:50.480
Thank you, everyone.

24:53.560 --> 24:55.020
Mu Qingyun isn't here yet.

24:55.600 --> 24:57.000
What kind of person is he?

25:07.200 --> 25:09.560
Next, please welcome the final group.

25:09.720 --> 25:12.040
Mu Qingyun, Xing Yaqi.

25:17.440 --> 25:19.240
Take another half step forward,

25:19.400 --> 25:20.560
and I'll kill you.

25:22.000 --> 25:23.240
You should do this.

25:24.640 --> 25:25.800
And I deserve to die.

25:27.080 --> 25:28.640
There was once a sincere love

25:28.640 --> 25:29.800
placed before me,

25:30.840 --> 25:32.170
but I didn't cherish it.

25:34.080 --> 25:36.600
Yuanbao really can't play Fairy Zixia anymore.

25:36.600 --> 25:37.760
Will she be sad?

25:38.960 --> 25:40.720
Yuanbao has been working so hard lately.

25:40.720 --> 25:42.450
I've been memorizing for days,

25:42.720 --> 25:44.720
but I can't even memorize a few lines,

25:44.720 --> 25:46.250
let alone perform on stage.

25:46.960 --> 25:48.120
I suddenly feel like

25:48.920 --> 25:50.680
I can't do anything right.

25:52.600 --> 25:54.640
All I do is daydream all day.

26:04.520 --> 26:06.200
Why isn't he saying anything?

26:07.080 --> 26:09.480
Did he get too nervous and forget his lines?

26:10.240 --> 26:11.000
No way.

26:11.040 --> 26:12.600
I saw him running lines with the class monitor a couple of days ago,

26:12.600 --> 26:13.840
and he was really fluent.

26:13.840 --> 26:14.720
In that case,

26:15.160 --> 26:16.240
then why did he...

26:19.880 --> 26:20.800
I...

26:22.440 --> 26:23.680
forgot my lines.

26:32.160 --> 26:32.760
It's okay.

26:33.000 --> 26:34.000
Take a moment to prepare,

26:34.000 --> 26:35.130
and let's try again.

26:36.040 --> 26:37.240
Um, Mr. Tian,

26:37.880 --> 26:39.010
no need to try again.

26:39.200 --> 26:40.600
I don't think I'm capable

26:40.600 --> 26:42.460
of playing the role of Zhi Zun Bao.

26:48.960 --> 26:49.840
Yaqi.

26:50.600 --> 26:51.400
I'm sorry

26:52.080 --> 26:53.340
for dragging you down.

26:54.120 --> 26:56.160
Qingyun, are you okay?

26:57.040 --> 26:57.760
I'm fine.

27:16.520 --> 27:19.240
Mr. Tian, I just remembered

27:19.480 --> 27:21.360
I have a vocal grading exam.

27:21.760 --> 27:22.880
So,

27:23.640 --> 27:24.700
I can't act either.

27:24.800 --> 27:26.560
Okay.

27:26.760 --> 27:27.440
Okay.

27:27.600 --> 27:29.400
Jingu, congratulations.

28:04.960 --> 28:06.280
Where did you go today?

28:06.520 --> 28:07.880
I sent you so many messages,

28:07.880 --> 28:09.080
but you didn't reply.

28:10.520 --> 28:12.720
I was playing games. I didn't see them.

28:13.960 --> 28:16.240
Didn't you swear a few days ago

28:16.280 --> 28:18.010
that you would beat Meng Jingu?

28:18.440 --> 28:20.370
Why did you suddenly give up today?

28:21.120 --> 28:23.380
What's wrong? Is something on your mind?

28:24.080 --> 28:24.680
Nothing.

28:25.520 --> 28:27.920
I just suddenly didn't want to act anymore.

28:28.000 --> 28:30.400
Congratulations. You got what you wanted.

28:33.040 --> 28:35.440
If you and Yaqi had participated,

28:37.240 --> 28:39.500
I probably wouldn't have stood a chance.

28:42.280 --> 28:42.960
Wait.

28:44.120 --> 28:47.080
Did you withdraw just so

28:47.280 --> 28:48.600
I could win?

28:52.000 --> 28:53.560
You wish.

28:54.640 --> 28:56.720
You know I've never liked

28:57.000 --> 28:58.530
these kinds of activities.

28:59.280 --> 29:00.000
Besides,

29:00.520 --> 29:02.120
I'm the top guy at Zhicheng.

29:03.200 --> 29:04.800
Why would I act like an idiot

29:04.840 --> 29:06.280
and play a monkey?

29:07.560 --> 29:08.160
See,

29:08.840 --> 29:09.880
I knew it.

29:09.920 --> 29:11.560
You've always been like this.

29:11.560 --> 29:13.760
When you suddenly said you were going to participate,

29:13.760 --> 29:14.920
I was confused.

29:15.880 --> 29:17.340
Now you're back to normal.

29:18.000 --> 29:18.720
By the way,

29:19.400 --> 29:20.600
I didn't tell Grandma

29:20.680 --> 29:23.040
that I was staying at school to rehearse the play.

29:23.040 --> 29:24.320
I just told her

29:24.680 --> 29:26.740
Meng Jingu was tutoring me at school.

29:27.320 --> 29:29.250
You have to keep this secret for me.

29:32.280 --> 29:33.120
I got it.

29:34.360 --> 29:37.240
Why are you agreeing so easily today?

29:39.080 --> 29:41.280
Let's go home.

29:46.920 --> 29:48.280
Grandma, I'm back.

29:49.760 --> 29:50.800
Yuanbao is back.

29:50.920 --> 29:52.880
Go wash your hands. We'll eat soon.

30:01.800 --> 30:03.260
Thank you for the clothes.

30:05.760 --> 30:07.560
These clothes really look good.

30:07.600 --> 30:10.130
I didn't expect you to rent clothes yourself.

30:13.240 --> 30:14.480
Yeah, yeah.

30:37.760 --> 30:39.560
Grandma, I'm going out for a bit.

30:55.000 --> 30:55.960
Eight thirty.

30:56.320 --> 30:58.280
I'll wait for you at Jufeng Billiards Hall.

30:58.280 --> 30:59.240
See you there.

31:22.560 --> 31:23.320
Hello, boss.

31:23.520 --> 31:24.320
I want to ask,

31:24.400 --> 31:26.200
was this rented here?

31:26.680 --> 31:27.520
It's ours.

31:27.600 --> 31:28.800
Are you returning it?

31:29.320 --> 31:31.760
I want to check the rental record

31:31.880 --> 31:33.140
to see when it expires.

31:33.600 --> 31:35.160
I want to rent more clothes.

31:35.280 --> 31:36.800
Okay, wait a moment.

31:40.280 --> 31:42.010
There are still a few days left.

31:43.760 --> 31:44.360
Here.
